 h-[1.2rem] w-[1.2rem] rotate-90 scale-0 transition-all dark:rotate-0 dark:scale-100 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button><a href=\"https://wa.me/2348137941914?text=Hi%20The%20Startup%20Desk%2C%20I&#x27;d%20like%20to%20talk%20about%20compliance%20for%20my%20startup.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-whatsapp bg-whatsapp px-3.5 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-whatsapp-foreground transition-colors hover:bg-whatsapp/90\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719\"></path></svg>Talk to us</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 md:hidden relative z-[60]\"><button class=\"relative inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-primary/10 bg-white/80 dark:bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm text-primary transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105\" aria-label=\"Toggle visual theme mode\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun h-[1.2rem] w-[1.2rem] rotate-0 scale-100 transition-all dark:-rotate-90 dark:scale-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute h-[1.2rem] w-[1.2rem] rotate-90 scale-0 transition-all dark:rotate-0 dark:scale-100 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border bg-white dark:bg-black text-foreground transition-all focus:outline-none\" aria-label=\"Toggle Navigation Menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-3xl py-16 text-center md:py-20\"><span class=\"animate-fade-in-up inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border bg-muted px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\" style=\"animation-delay:60ms\"><span class=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span>Pricing &amp; tiers</span><h1 class=\"animate-fade-in-up mt-6 font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-balance text-foreground sm:text-5xl\" style=\"animation-delay:140ms\">Compliance, handled at every stage.</h1><p class=\"animate-fade-in-up mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-pretty text-muted-foreground\" style=\"animation-delay:220ms\">Whether you just got your CAC certificate or you&#x27;re gearing up for your first raise, there&#x27;s a tier built for exactly where you are.</p></div></div></div><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-8 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid items-start gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border p-7 shadow-sm border-border bg-card\" style=\"animation-delay:120ms\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/8 text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rocket h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09\"></path><path d=\"M9 12a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.4 22.4 0 0 1-4 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 .05 5 .05\"></path></svg></span></div><p class=\"mt-5 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-accent\">Launch</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">For founders just getting started</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-display text-xl font-bold leading-snug text-balance text-foreground\">Get compliant from day one — not after something goes wrong.</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-pretty text-muted-foreground\">Most compliance problems start in the first 90 days — a missed registration, a document filed wrong, a step nobody told you about. Launch handles the essentials so your company is properly set up from the start, not patched together later.</p><div class=\"mt-6\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">What&#x27;s included</p><ul class=\"mt-3 flex flex-col gap-2.5\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">CAC post-incorporation filing</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Statutory registers setup</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">FIRS tax registration (TIN)</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Compliance starter checklist for your specific business type</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Optional: brand identity add-on (logo, basic style guide)</span></li></ul></div><p class=\"mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Who it&#x27;s for: </span>Newly incorporated companies, first few months in.</p><div class=\"mt-auto pt-7\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-1.5\"><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">From</span><span class=\"font-display text-2xl font-bold text-foreground\">₦75,000</span></div><a href=\"https://wa.me/2348137941914?text=Hi%20The%20Startup%20Desk%2C%20I&#x27;m%20interested%20in%20the%20Launch%20package%20for%20my%20newly%20incorporated%20company.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group mt-4 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background border border-primary/25 text-primary hover:bg-primary/5 focus-visible:ring-primary\">Get Started<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border p-7 shadow-sm border-primary bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-xl lg:-mt-4\" style=\"animation-delay:220ms\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary-foreground/10 text-accent\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-radar h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19.07 4.93A10 10 0 0 0 6.99 3.34\"></path><path d=\"M4 6h.01\"></path><path d=\"M2.29 9.62A10 10 0 1 0 21.31 8.35\"></path><path d=\"M16.24 7.76A6 6 0 1 0 8.23 16.67\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M17.99 11.66A6 6 0 0 1 15.77 16.67\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"m13.41 10.59 5.66-5.66\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-accent px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-accent-foreground\">Most popular</span></div><p class=\"mt-5 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-accent\">Monitoring</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-primary-foreground/70\">For founders who don&#x27;t want to think about deadlines</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-display text-xl font-bold leading-snug text-balance text-primary-foreground\">Stay compliant, automatically.</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-pretty text-primary-foreground/75\">Annual returns. Register updates. Renewal deadlines. None of these are complicated on their own — but miss enough of them and CAC can strike your company off. Monitoring means someone&#x27;s watching your compliance calendar so you don&#x27;t have to.</p><div class=\"mt-6\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary-foreground/60\">What&#x27;s included</p><ul class=\"mt-3 flex flex-col gap-2.5\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-primary-foreground/90\">Annual returns tracking and filing</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-primary-foreground/90\">Statutory register updates</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-primary-foreground/90\">Deadline reminders before they become problems</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-primary-foreground/90\">Ongoing regulatory check-ins</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-primary-foreground/90\">Priority WhatsApp access for compliance questions</span></li></ul></div><p class=\"mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-primary-foreground/70\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Who it&#x27;s for: </span>Companies 6+ months in, already operating, want it off their plate.</p><div class=\"mt-auto pt-7\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-1.5\"><span class=\"text-sm text-primary-foreground/60\">From</span><span class=\"font-display text-2xl font-bold text-primary-foreground\">₦12,000/mo</span></div><a href=\"https://wa.me/2348137941914?text=Hi%20The%20Startup%20Desk%2C%20I&#x27;d%20like%20to%20set%20up%20the%20Monitoring%20plan%20to%20stay%20on%20top%20of%20my%20filings%20and%20deadlines.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group mt-4 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background bg-accent text-accent-foreground shadow-sm hover:brightness-105 hover:shadow-md focus-visible:ring-accent\">Subscribe<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border p-7 shadow-sm border-border bg-card\" style=\"animation-delay:320ms\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/8 text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></span></div><p class=\"mt-5 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-accent\">Advisory</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">For founders scaling, hiring, or raising</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-display text-xl font-bold leading-snug text-balance text-foreground\">The compliance layer that comes with growth.</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-pretty text-muted-foreground\">Hiring your first employees, handling customer data, entering a regulated sector, or prepping for investor due diligence all bring compliance requirements most founders don&#x27;t see coming until it costs them a deal. Advisory is built around your specific stage and sector — scoped to what you actually need, not a generic package.</p><div class=\"mt-6\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">What&#x27;s included (scoped per engagement)</p><ul class=\"mt-3 flex flex-col gap-2.5\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">NDPA / data protection compliance programs</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Employment contracts and HR structuring</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Sector-specific licensing guidance</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Investor-readiness compliance audits</span></li></ul></div><p class=\"mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Who it&#x27;s for: </span>Funded, hiring, or scaling startups with more complex needs.</p><div class=\"mt-auto pt-7\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-1.5\"><span class=\"font-display text-2xl font-bold text-foreground\">Custom scope</span></div><a href=\"https://wa.me/2348137941914?text=Hi%20The%20Startup%20Desk%2C%20I&#x27;d%20like%20to%20book%20an%20Advisory%20consultation%20about%20compliance%20for%20my%20scaling%20startup.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group mt-4 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-5 py-3 text-base font-semibold transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background border border-primary/25 text-primary hover:bg-primary/5 focus-visible:ring-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719\"></path></svg>Book a Consultation</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card\"><table class=\"w-full text-left text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-border bg-muted/50\"><th class=\"p-4 font-medium text-muted-foreground\"></th><th class=\"p-4 font-display font-semibold text-foreground\">Launch</th><th class=\"p-4 font-display font-semibold text-foreground\">Monitoring</th><th class=\"p-4 font-display font-semibold text-foreground\">Advisory</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-border last:border-0\"><td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Best for</td><td class=\"p-4 text-foreground\">Just incorporated</td><td class=\"p-4 text-foreground\">Ongoing operations</td><td class=\"p-4 text-foreground\">Scaling / raising</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border last:border-0\"><td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Commitment</td><td class=\"p-4 text-foreground\">One-off</td><td class=\"p-4 text-foreground\">Monthly</td><td class=\"p-4 text-foreground\">Project-based</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border last:border-0\"><td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Starting price</td><td class=\"p-4 text-foreground\">₦75,000</td><td class=\"p-4 text-foreground\">₦12,000/mo</td><td class=\"p-4 text-foreground\">Custom</td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-16 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up mx-auto max-w-3xl rounded-2xl border border-border bg-muted/40 p-8 text-center md:p-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-balance text-foreground sm:text-3xl\">Not a law firm. Not trying to be.</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-pretty text-muted-foreground\">The Startup Desk is a compliance consultancy — we handle filings, documentation, and regulatory guidance. For anything that requires actual legal representation, we&#x27;ll point you to a licensed lawyer we trust. Most of what trips founders up isn&#x27;t a legal battle — it&#x27;s paperwork done wrong or filed late. That&#x27;s what we fix.</p></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-primary px-6 py-14 text-center text-primary-foreground shadow-xl md:px-12\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0\"><div class=\"absolute -right-16 -top-16 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-accent/10\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-20 -left-10 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-primary-foreground/5\"></div></div><div class=\"relative\"><h2 class=\"mx-auto max-w-2xl font-display text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-balance sm:text-4xl\">Not sure which tier fits? Let&#x27;s figure it out together.</h2><div class=\"mt-8 flex justify-center\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/2348137941914?text=Hi%20The%20Startup%20Desk%2C%20I&#x27;m%20not%20sure%20which%20tier%20fits%20my%20startup%20%E2%80%94%20can%20you%20help%20me%20figure%20it%20out%3F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-accent px-7 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-accent-foreground shadow-sm transition-all hover:brightness-105 hover:shadow-md focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1